So, she'll make a little pair of dungarees with corduroys, with African material mixed in. Very creative designs,
has reached a stage where she even had an order from Wal-Mart.
For 10,000 pieces.
So that shows you that we have people who are capable of doing.
And the women are diligent. They are focused; they work hard.
