So my second dream is that I think we can look to the next 30 years as a time to change the food system again.
And we know what's happened in the past, so if we start now, and we look at technologies and improvements to the food system long term, we might be able to recreate the food system
so when I give my next talk and I'm 60 years old, I'll be able to say that it's been a success.
